{"tid":1460243,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"林鄭:香港國際機場有幾重要，我諗唔需要多講。","createTime":"2019-08-13T02:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T02:17:54.000Z","uid":249846,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4a59a6a117abc4dff6b9e38b30cdb2ee4a9fa9f0","tid":1460243,"uid":249846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"各位手足大家識做啦？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有班手足係機場幫我地頂左成晚<br />\n到今時今日仲講緊示威者暴力？<br />\n諗住做下支線任務　點知觸發隱藏主線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲同我講話示威者搞到警察家屬，搞到市民？<br />\n邊撚個係地鐵站放催淚彈阿？係邊個射撚爆人地隻眼？邊個撚個放任黑社會打香港人阿仆街？<br />\n一篇文邊到講得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解市民會咁驚？<br />\n又玩倒果為因呢招阿？<br />\n最撚嬲係　佢已經完全失明，你同我講希望佢早康復？<br />\n我地對唔對得住已經犧牲既手足？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果呢一刻放棄，我地失去既永遠都拎唔到。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1XijLh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1XijLh.png&h=154ea46f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12415669b1d012dbc66a21d9548e5e1fdbbec706","tid":1460243,"uid":4948,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0t3ckk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0t3ckk.png&h=6afdf073&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f15a9ed7640785bdffe1eb12b28350d2e073cd8a","tid":1460243,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48729e19f887de4fe7